{
  "stem": "20686.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remembered that before the war in 1938, there was a play staged in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't remember by whom.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was the [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And when I put on that yellow patch, that play came back to my-- to me like a, a reflex, that all of a sudden, I'm taken back to the Middle Ages.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] But I did not feel the shame of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I, I felt, rather, they should feel, feel ashamed of making people putting on yellow stars, yellow patches.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I, I, I, I-- not even shame-- I thought this-- it's, it's a, a stupid move.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It does not belong.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It does not belong in, in, in our society, amongst people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Despite all the anti-Semitisms, despite everything which took place, I taught this is out of context.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Germans realized-- they already had a plan to transform this ghetto them into a giant-- gigantic, industrial center [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] where they can get things made perfectly well-- beautiful things made for no money.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They don't have to pay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just get to give a piece of bread and a-- and a thin soup, a potato or a vegetable.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's, that's what took place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked in a clothing factory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--making uniforms for the German Army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They also were involved, all in German industry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They made millions.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Billions they took out from, from, from, from our sweat and work, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes they talk about this restitution money we're getting now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is so stupid.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
